  "name": "snowacle_qualify",
  "notes": "Row limiting uses QUALIFY with a window-function predicate (modeled here via limit_syntax=sample_n with limit_keyword=QUALIFY). CTEs use DEFINE instead of WITH. The null-safe equality operator is spelled IS SAME AS. NULLS FIRST is the immutable default for both ASC and DESC ordering. Modulo uses the keyword MOD (Oracle style). Semicolons are required. Window default frame is ROWS UNBOUNDED TO CURRENT (Snowflake-like). Array indexing is 1-based (Oracle/Snowflake).",
